descriptionHtml:
This extends the alchemists shack to be more interesting, and all containers are no-respawning. Near the shack is a secret door that also leads to a bonus cave house with a very good merchant! I will upload images soon.

Features in version 1 are-

-Smithy in the back
-Weapon racks (Not working for some reason at the moment)
-front garden with ingredients
-Secret bonus house with secret bonus weapon and secret bonus merchant :D

Bugs- 
-To get out of the secret area, you must use the console command TCL and fly behind the door and then activate it. I will fix this soon.
-The secret weapon can only be held in the right hand or it will glitch.
